Name: The Guild Garage
Title: Choppin' Tops
Desc: David and Larry visit Keith Dean and search for a car at the Pomona Swap Meet and Classic Car Show.
LongDescription: David and Larry visit Keith Dean, a Southern California car builder known for his unique designs and movie cars; Larry loves Keith's work, so they search for a donor car at the Pomona Swap Meet and Classic Car Show for Larry's project with Keith.
